import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import "./styles/GrowthTable.css"; const GrowthTable = ({ character, gameClass, expertise, starsphere }) => { const characterName = "Alear"; const gameClassName = "Divine Child" const growthTotals = { hp: 10, str: 10, mag: 10, dex: 10, spd: 10, def: 10, res: 10, lck: 10, bld: 10, } const expertiseGrowths = expertise? 15 : 0 const starsphereGrowths = starsphere? 15 : 0 return (
{characterName} | {gameClassName} Base Class Expertise Starsphere TOTAL
HP {starsphereGrowths} {growthTotals.hp}
STR {starsphereGrowths} {growthTotals.str}
MAG {starsphereGrowths} {growthTotals.mag}
DEX {starsphereGrowths} {growthTotals.dex}
SPD {starsphereGrowths} {growthTotals.spd}
DEF {starsphereGrowths} {growthTotals.def}
RES {starsphereGrowths} {growthTotals.res}
LCK {starsphereGrowths} {growthTotals.lck}
BLD {starsphereGrowths} {growthTotals.bld}
) } export default GrowthTable;
